    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable, super fun ride that's been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure? You\u2019ve found it! This beauty runs like a dream and is in great shape overall\u2014perfect for your daily commute or those long weekend getaways. It\u2019s been well-maintained, has plenty of life left in it, and is just waiting for a new home. Come take it for a spin and see why I've enjoyed it so much!",
