    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E92-generation M3, featuring the legendary S65B40 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This high-revving powerplant delivers 414 hp with a soaring 8,400 RPM redline, managed by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. The chassis retains its factory-tuned kinematics, offering exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive analysis of the individual throttle bodies and a cooling system refresh. The rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed, ensuring the longitudinal and transverse dynamics remain uncompromised. This is a mechanically robust example of the last atmospheric M3, ready for spirited canyon runs or track day duty.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
