      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s still got so much life left in her! It\u2019s been a fantastic car\u2014really solid, reliable, and honestly just a joy to drive. It\u2019s been well-loved and is in great shape for its next owner. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable set of wheels that feels just right, this is the one. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come say hi and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 straight-six. This example features a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the double-VANOS system has been serviced to maintain optimal cam timing. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, providing the tactile feedback expected of this chassis. While it shows the honest patina of a driven car, the powertrain remains robust with linear power delivery and no rod bearing issues. A perfect candidate for a driver-focused enthusiast looking for a balanced, high-performance platform.",
